{"tid":699821,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"《美女廚房》否認虐待動物","createTime":"2018-06-13T00:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T06:37:15.000Z","uid":82917,"like":297,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2c61195fafe7668776f0454a9c14cabcfc3bd0","tid":699821,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/081551_279efd59e98c06f8e1cc88af2a3095fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F13%2F081551_279efd59e98c06f8e1cc88af2a3095fb.png&h=c89bd004&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n■（左起）蕭正楠、阿Bob、張振朗與周中，堅信《美女廚房》不會被腰斬。<br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】對於新一輯《美女廚房》再被指虐待動物及浪費食物等投訴，主持蕭正楠、林盛斌（Bob）與張振朗昨日出席活動時，直言會根據觀眾意見去調整及改善，澄清完全沒有意圖虐待動物。阿蕭解釋現場有熟手師傅幫參賽者處理食物，讓所有動物不至於死得痛苦，只是一直不想將幕後秘密公告天下而已。他又指每次吃剩的食物也會有工作人員打包，相當「惜食」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，談到《美女廚房》是非多多兼劣評如潮，節目播出兩集，通訊事務管理局已收逾800宗投訴，三人堅信節目不會被腰斬，並謂每集的質素也有進步，<span style=\"color: red;\">甚至有嘉賓感動到喊。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n喊乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a42ac6480f9b34075d495594f1a29d0846218521","tid":699821,"uid":35701,"like":295,"dislike":1,"score":294,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:18:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6fa9be76364ca879e7615177bc738e88b09fcc3","tid":699821,"uid":112747,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:20:22.000Z","msg":"張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a347cd931f49c7b0feb2debe08a9b0ddb212a16e","tid":699821,"uid":44277,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"2e2c61195fafe7668776f0454a9c14cabcfc3bd0","tid":699821,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:17:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/13/081551_279e