不想將幕後秘密公告天下而已。他又指每次吃剩的食物也會有工作人員打包，相當「惜食」。<br />\n<br />\n此外，談到《美女廚房》是非多多兼劣評如潮，節目播出兩集，通訊事務管理局已收逾800宗投訴，三人堅信節目不會被腰斬，並謂每集的質素也有進步，<span style=\"color: red;\">甚至有嘉賓感動到喊。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n喊乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:20:29.000Z","msg":"難食到喊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:26:47.000Z","msg":"柒頭卜勁撚造作，成碟野倒落垃圾桶<br />\n唔撚好笑喎<br />\nRonald個啲好撚真心<br />\n佢就假撚到死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T02:59:02.000Z","msg":"記得以前睇有集鄭中基拎碟炒蛋當泥膠玩笑到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e5630f3a31bd30cfeecaa8bdd2f831048b353f","tid":699821,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:21:53.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"645c2df318da304f9f2fb4d0999aced28f27ef95","tid":699821,"uid":100737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:53:24.000Z","msg":"又毁一經典"},{"pid":"6930aafac546e86a307944e3a47a2414e8173fac","tid":699821,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c99e2303d7ebe96ffb000011f2db58198e14341b","tid":699821,"uid":48222,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4d2f8502148ee663fb6d92ea67716945789fdd6c","tid":699821,"uid":82917,"like":111,"dislike":1,"score":110,"quote":{"pid":"a347cd931f49c7b0feb2debe08a9b0ddb212a16e","tid":699821,"uid":44277,"like":35,"dislike":2,"score":33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T00:20:29.000Z","msg":"難食到喊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201